es/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n廢牌係咪咁撚敏感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> on9仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大家鬥貼車牌睇吓邊個冧把多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n甩咗P未呀</blockquote><br />\n唔係1 2最多咪考到老電牌，中型以上都要棍啦<br />\n<br />\n定係你揸的士<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/24/180434_74c59f8327f57392684b07c8b2f52d3b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F24%2F180434_74c59f8327f57392684b07c8b2f52d3b.jpg&h=5b6cceed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我考車牌時，駕駛學院仲喺黃竹坑呀</blockquote><br />\n咁人地冇寸你，你咩事咁大反應？</blockquote><br />\n其實佢第一句根本無諗住串人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只係有傻仔睇唔明佢講「2腳極力子」點解,以為人地串緊佢啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nPS.要用2腳極力子嘅車,其實得大型車先要<br />\n其實已經表明佢有18以上嘅牌,然後個傻仔以為人地廢牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb82a6c7f2f014f8f8be2045d77b62a7edff3264","tid":132653,"uid":7291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T03:28:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n2號牌俾盡你咪小學雞。<br />\n<br />\n考咗2腳極力子再返嚟嘈啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n純統計呀 屌你老母 我鬼有嘈呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n廢牌係咪咁撚敏感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> on9仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大家鬥貼車牌睇吓邊個冧把多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class